      <title>佩特罗总统表示哥伦比亚将切断与以色列的外交关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/president-petro-says-colombia-to-cut-diplomatic-ties-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗在周三的劳动节假期演讲中表示，哥伦比亚将与以色列断绝外交关系，因为以色列有“一位种族灭绝的总统”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/president-petro-says-colombia-to-cut-diplomatic-ties-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:03:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因支持俄罗斯战争而制裁中国和阿联酋的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-sanctions-firms-in-china-uae-for-support-of-russia-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国周三宣布对包括中国和阿拉伯联合酋长国在内的近 300 家公司和个人实施制裁，理由是它们涉嫌支持俄罗斯入侵乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-sanctions-firms-in-china-uae-for-support-of-russia-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国监管机构讨论最早于八月敲定银行资本规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一些批评人士呼吁废除该计划，但美联储和其他美国顶级监管机构仍在推进其具有里程碑意义的计划，该计划旨在让大银行持有更多资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院议长反对快速通道银行业务和稳定币票据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/pot-banking-stablecoin-bills-hit-hurdles-with-speaker-johnson</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会快速审议向大麻企业开放银行服务、监管稳定币并促进信用卡刷卡费用竞争的立法前景黯淡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/pot-banking-stablecoin-bills-hit-hurdles-with-speaker-johnson</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:17:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>皮尤研究中心称更多美国人视中国为敌人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/more-americans-consider-china-an-enemy-pew-research-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皮尤研究中心的一项调查显示，美国人越来越将中国视为敌人，大多数人认为限制北京的权力和影响力应该是美国外交政策的首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/more-americans-consider-china-an-enemy-pew-research-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么抵押贷款和利率是英国选举的热门问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/why-mortgages-interest-rates-and-house-prices-are-a-hot-uk-election-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国预计今年晚些时候举行大选，执政的保守党和反对党工党正在制定相互竞争的计划来帮助关键人群：有抱负的房主。几十年来住房投资不足造成的负担能力危机因持续高利率而雪上加霜，这增加了借款人转抵押房产的成本。住房成本上涨的部分原因是前总理利兹·特拉斯和保守党领导下的经济管理不善]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/why-mortgages-interest-rates-and-house-prices-are-a-hot-uk-election-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富国银行、加拿大皇家银行银行家会见德克萨斯州股份公司员工，讨论 ESG 调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/wells-fargo-rbc-bankers-visit-texas-ag-s-office-amid-esg-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州总检察长的工作人员会见了富国银行和纽约市的市政财务主管。肯·帕克斯顿 (Ken Paxton) 对华尔街银行是否“抵制”化石燃料行业的调查仍在拖延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/wells-fargo-rbc-bankers-visit-texas-ag-s-office-amid-esg-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:21:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党强硬派强制投票罢免议长约翰逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gop-hardliners-plan-to-force-vote-on-deposing-speaker-johnson</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名共和党强硬派周三宣布，他们将强制投票罢免众议院议长迈克·约翰逊(Mike Johnson)，这场战斗他们几乎肯定会失败，同时会在一个严重分裂的政党中激起意识形态敌意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gop-hardliners-plan-to-force-vote-on-deposing-speaker-johnson</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约警察局在大学校园镇压中逮捕了 300 多名抗议者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ny-police-amass-near-columbia-as-adams-tells-protesters-to-leave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对以色列与哈马斯战争的愤怒，纽约警察驱散了两所大学不断升级的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动，逮捕了近 300 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ny-police-amass-near-columbia-as-adams-tells-protesters-to-leave</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 01:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议院通过俄罗斯铀进口禁令，送交拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/senate-passes-russian-uranium-import-ban-sending-bill-to-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院周二晚上投票通过了禁止从俄罗斯进口浓缩铀的立法，并将该措施发送给总统。据白宫称，乔·拜登总统计划很快将其签署成为法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/senate-passes-russian-uranium-import-ban-sending-bill-to-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 23:01:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
